snippet.title: Two Point Hospital: Culture Shock | OUT NOW!
snippet.description:
Our new DLC, Two Point Hospital Culture Shock is OUT NOW on Steam!

Two Point Hospital Culture Shock is out now for £6.99/$8.99/€8.99 (prices may vary depending on your region).

Two Point County is having an artistic crisis. The creative world is bereft of ideas. Culture is drying up, and nothing is left but a crusty nubbin and an uninspiring husk.

Fortunately, you’re on hand to answer the call of artist-in-residence Zara Fitzpocket, chief guardian of all things arty and the county’s very own culture vulture, as she seeks to resuscitate the music scene, the silver screen and all artwork in between, in our brand new DLC Two Point Hospital: Culture Shock, available for pre-purchase now with a juicy 10% discount!
